<item>
            <title>[LU-4671] sanity test_43: multiop still running</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4671</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a660bd44-9e05-11e3-a567-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a660bd44-9e05-11e3-a567-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4671#&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4671#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
This was hit so far only one time for testing &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3336&quot; title=&quot;LFSCK II: MDT-OST OST orphan handling&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3336&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3336&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/8305&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/8305&lt;/a&gt;, so it may be related to that patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_43 failed with the following error in the test output:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;multiop still running&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The test itself correctly returned &quot;f43.sanity: Text file busy&quot;, but there was nothing else in the log.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 43&lt;/p&gt;</description>
